defaultMedia freedom defaultupdatedefault&#xa0;defaultMedia freedom issues continue 
defaultto affect the BBC’s ability to reach its audiences.
default&#xa0;
default 
defaultMany of these issues were 
defaultdescribed in detail
default in BBC World Service’s written evidence submitted to the FAC’
defaults Human Rights inquiry.  This is a
