defaultJanuary 2015. As a result of this support MRTV now has its first prime-time politics programme to feature interviews with members of all the parties represented in Parliament, a new radio current affairs programmes featuring differing points of view and an
default emerging newsgathering structure that is more independent than anything the country has known in the past few decades .
